=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">申請表都唔識填 點寫排版</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄2014 西方日報 不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三次不合格 失重考資格</span><br />\n<br />\n在內地任職護士逾十年的陳女士來港後，以海外護士資歷申請報考香港護士管理局的登記護士執業試。該考試要求若考生三次不能通過執業試，包括筆試及實習試，除非得到特別許可，否則會失去重考資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳聲稱通過筆試後，卻在實習試的考核中遭不公平待遇。她指，實習試要求考生在一小時內完成兩至三項操作，如<span class=\"red\">洗傷口、包紮及攙扶病人</span>等，惟考室規則各有不同，考核前並無通知考生。「A考室畀你一個鐘內做晒所有操作；B考室就要求每個操作做三十分鐘，時間冇得累積」。她指，考室的<span class=\"red\">洗手盆過低</span>，亦令考生難以符合無菌洗手的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">三十分鐘一個都完成唔到 好意思投訴考試不公</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">簡單扶抱都唔掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎到香港只會幫倒忙 <br />\n多謝曬中國資深護士</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce2340e709fe7198d69d04db958cc1fecd2135fa","tid":2122056,"uid":236993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff7bcd52e6c2162165d43ea78e4a6e36c9549faa","tid":2122056,"uid":358333,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:46:54.000Z","msg":"：唔好<br />\n：停<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3f74df7577d12ec94dfc68b361e30877f3c87c","tid":2122056,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:58:59.000Z","msg":"快去英國NHS喇"},{"pid":"cdd8f9c2044ed994ffc6ce7ccf85c60e23ed1f20","tid":2122056,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T23:35:54.000Z","msg":"哇成班p牌blame the victim<br />\n就好似香港爆武漢肺炎係香港人問題唔係政府問題咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9db2a9a9e67da288b62ccc3017362f0e8d9413","tid":2122056,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T23:42:09.000Z","msg":"好多人騎牛搵馬 大把人走"},{"